<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_c987db20a4d7.aspx"><b>赠刘景文</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%ae%8b%e4%bb%a3">宋代</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e8%8b%8f%e8%bd%bc">苏轼</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonc987db20a4d7">
<p>荷尽已无擎雨盖，菊残犹有傲霜枝。<br />一年好景君须记，最是橙黄橘绿时。(最是 一作：正是) </p>
</div>
</div>
