<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_8f1be8b774c2.aspx"><b>雪梅·其一</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%ae%8b%e4%bb%a3">宋代</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e5%8d%a2%e6%a2%85%e5%9d%a1">卢梅坡</a></p>
